  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559070/extras/c14dacbf8c3d8c88639dace4cb659207.poster.avif?t=1739942612\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559070/extras/c14dacbf8c3d8c88639dace4cb659207.webm?t=1739942612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559070/extras/c14dacbf8c3d8c88639dace4cb659207.mp4?t=1739942612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DODGE OR DIE 💀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn to Dodge</strong> is a<i> bullet hell dodging game</i> from Timeflier Games. Inspired by games such as Realm of the Mad God and Warcraft 3's Run Kitty Run. Each map has three difficulties as to let gamers of all dodging skills to progress to the end. The game contains: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 maps with 3 difficulties each, as well as a prologue and two epilogues, for a total of 15 maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 challenge maps with 3 difficulties each, shorter and tougher levels! More challenges will be added.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each map has TWO leaderboards (fastest, and fastest untouchable), as well as the ability to select a player's best time and a race their ghost to the finish. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over a dozen hazards, such as grenades, spiders, trapdoors, and slime! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collectibles placed on each level, including coins that you can spend on skins! </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559070/extras/c14dacbf8c3d8c88639dace4cb659207.poster.avif?t=1739942612\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559070/extras/c14dacbf8c3d8c88639dace4cb659207.webm?t=1739942612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559070/extras/c14dacbf8c3d8c88639dace4cb659207.mp4?t=1739942612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DODGE OR DIE 💀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn to Dodge</strong> is a<i> bullet hell dodging game</i> from Timeflier Games. Inspired by games such as Realm of the Mad God and Warcraft 3's Run Kitty Run. Each map has three difficulties as to let gamers of all dodging skills to progress to the end. The game contains: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 maps with 3 difficulties each, as well as a prologue and two epilogues, for a total of 15 maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 challenge maps with 3 difficulties each, shorter and tougher levels! More challenges will be added.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each map has TWO leaderboards (fastest, and fastest untouchable), as well as the ability to select a player's best time and a race their ghost to the finish. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over a dozen hazards, such as grenades, spiders, trapdoors, and slime! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collectibles placed on each level, including coins that you can spend on skins! </p></li></ul>",
